en-US.title: UP Health System
en-US.description: UP Health System is a local health care provider that offers a wide range of medical services. This organization is dedicated to providing quality health care for everyone in the community, including those in the transgender community. They provide a safe, non-judgmental environment where individuals can receive care that is sensitive to their needs.

address: 1414 W Fair Ave # 36, Marquette, MI 49855, USA
